## RTL Language Support

RTL support needed for: {{ profile.i18n.rtl_languages | join(", ") }}

> Use CSS logical properties (margin-inline-start, padding-inline-end) instead of physical properties (margin-left, padding-right). Set dir="rtl" on the root element for RTL locales.
