## Rules

1. **NEVER** hardcode user-facing strings — always use the i18n framework
2. Keep translation keys organized and hierarchical
3. Add translations for all supported locales when introducing new strings
{% if profile.i18n.i18n_framework %}
4. Use `{{ profile.i18n.i18n_framework }}` APIs — do not introduce alternative i18n solutions
{% endif %}

